nks%20Elon%20Musk%20is%20very%20cool%20because%20if%20you're%207%20years%20old%20and%20you%20saw%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-cybertruck-my-favorite-features-wireless-charging-speed-range-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECybertruck%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20you'd%20also%20think%20it%20was%20extremely%20cool.%20However%2C%20he%20and%20his%20peers%20have%20zero%20interest%20or%20awareness%20of%20the%20concept%20of%20X%20or%20Twitter.%20I%20know%20many%207-%20to%209-year-olds%3B%20I%20have%20never%20heard%20of%20any%20of%20them%20using%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EQustodio's%20report%20says%20that%20for%20this%20age%20range%2C%20Roblox%20is%20the%20most%20popular%20app%2C%20followed%20by%20YouTube.%20This%20sounds%20about%20right.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20X%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2257084681-09df-4e8f-a6ee-71fd43fe8437%5C%22%3EParents%20might%20be%20the%20ones%20actually%20using%20X%20%E2%80%94%20and%20Amazon%20Shopping%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20reached%20out%20to%20Qustodio%20to%20ask%20how%20to%20interpret%20this%20bizarre%20number.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmily%20Lawrenson%2C%20Qustodio's%20content%20and%20communication%20manager%2C%20told%20me%20that%20it%20%26quot%3Bdoesn't%20mean%20that%20kids%20are%20actively%20posting%20on%20X%3B%20simply%20that%2031%25%20of%20that%20age%20group%20used%20the%20app%20across%202023.%20We%20would%20be%20inclined%20to%20merit%20this%20to%20pure%20curiosity%20at%20this%20age.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20asked%20if%20perhaps%20this%20could%20be%20because%20a%20child%20was%20using%20a%20device%20that%20they%20shared%20with%20a%20grown-up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20considered%20the%20profile%20usage%20rather%20than%20the%20device%20itself%20to%20avoid%20this%2C%20as%20profiles%20on%20Qustodio%20are%20individual%20to%20each%20child%2C%26quot%3B%20Lawrenson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20important%20to%20note%20that%20access%20does%20not%20equate%20to%20engagement%3B%20rather%2C%20it%20can%20include%20having%20the%20application%20open%20and%20scrolling%20it.%20It's%20important%20to%20note%2C%20too%2C%20the%20ease%20with%20which%20X%20can%20be%20accessed%3B%20a%20simple%20search%20online%2C%20which%20children%20do%20regularly%2C%20about%20a%20particular%20topic%20of%20interest%20can%20yield%20an%20X%20result%2C%20which%2C%20once%20clicked%2C%20can%20prompt%20the%20child%20to%20download%20the%20application%20and%20view%20the%20application%2C%26quot%3B%20Lawrenson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20X%20app%20doesn't%20let%20you%20see%20tweets%20if%20you're%20not%20logged%20in%2C%20so%20it's%20not%20actually%20so%20easy%20to%20accidentally%20surf%20around.%20It's%20also%20rated%2017%2B%20in%20the%20App%20Store%20and%20Google%20Play%2C%20which%20means%20that%20if%20a%20parent%20has%20set%20up%20age%20limits%20for%20app%20downloads%2C%20it%20wouldn't%20be%20easy%20for%20the%20kid%20to%20simply%20get%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20a%20theory%3A%20Many%20parents%20probably%20set%20up%20their%20kids'%20iPads%20using%20their%20own%20adult%20iCloud%20account%20because%20iPads%20don't%20allow%20you%20to%20switch%20between%20more%20than%20one%20user%20account%2C%20and%20setting%20up%20a%20whole%20new%20iCloud%20account%20for%20a%20kid%20is%20a%20lot%20more%20work.%20(I%20recommend%20doing%20it%2C%20however%2C%20as%20it's%20worth%20the%20hassle!)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple's%20parental%20controls%20are%20robust%2C%20but%20require%20creating%20a%20new%20iCloud%20account%20(and%20creating%20a%20new%20email%20address%20for%20them)%2C%20attaching%20it%20as%20a%20child%20under%20a%20family%20plan%2C%20and%20then%20fiddling%20around%20with%20settings%20on%20both%20the%20parent%20and%20child%20devices.%20It's%20quite%20possible%20that%20some%20parents%20would%20rather%20use%20a%20third-party%20solution%20like%20Qustodio%20than%20deal%20with%20the%20slightly%20confusing%20Apple%20settings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20those%20cases%2C%20a%20parent%20might%20also%20occasionally%20use%20the%20iPad%2C%20and%20add%20things%20like%20X%2C%20even%20though%20the%20Qustodio%20profile%20would%20be%20for%20the%20child.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20hint%20that%20this%20might%20be%20the%20case%20is%20that%20Qustodio%20found%20the%20Amazon%20shopping%20app%20was%20used%20by%2041%25%20of%207-%20to%209-year-olds%2C%20even%20though%20it%2C%20like%20X%2C%20was%20only%20used%20for%20a%20few%20minutes%20per%20day%20on%20average.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESharing%20a%20device%20might%20explain%20why%20these%20adult%20apps%20are%20even%20available%20to%20kids%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2231848cdf-232c-4efc-940a-3b5cabd5198f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESo%20why%20does%20this%20even%20matter%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETech%20companies%20often%20put%20out%20reports%20with%20survey%20results%20or%20data%20analysis%20like%20this.%20It's%20a%20good%20way%20to%20get%20publicity%20and%20understand%20user%20behavior.%20I%20get%20PR%20pitches%20like%20this%20all%20the%20time%2C%20and%20sometimes%2C%20they%20are%20illuminating%20and%20interesting!%20A%20company%20that%20monitors%20kids'%20screen%20time%20would%20likely%20have%20some%20very%20interesting%20insights%20and%20data%20about%20an%20issue%20that%20is%20currently%20a%20huge%20conversation.%20(TechCrunch%20took%20Qustodio%20up%20on%20this%20report%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftechcrunch.com%2F2024%2F08%2F19%2Fa-surprising-number-of-ipad-kids-are-on-x-study-finds%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%20about%20it%3C%2Fa%3E.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20a%20company%20is%20writing%20these%20reports%20with%20its%20own%20data%20and%20methodology%2C%20you%20have%20to%20be%20a%20little%20skeptical.%20Qustodio%20wants%20to%20sell%20parents%20screentime%20monitoring%20software%20%E2%80%94%20it%20would%20be%20in%20the%20company's%20interest%20to%20play%20up%20the%20potential%20dangers%20of%20screentime.%20And%20yes%2C%20the%20idea%20of%20nearly%20a%20third%20of%207-%20to%209-year-olds%20being%20on%20X%20is%20very%20scary!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20think%20Qustodio%20just%20invented%20some%20fake%20numbers.%20But%20I%20think%20there%20might%20be%20more%20to%20the%20story%20about%20what%20is%20going%20on%20behind%20this%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20shows%20that%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20screen%20time%20and%20kids%2C%20there's%20just%20a%20lot%20we%20don't%20know.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsecond-graders-using-x-parental-controls-2024-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724414401000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c7ae301aa2ac29ee3389ca%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsecond-graders-using-x-parental-controls-2024-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20report%20just%20came%20out%20saying%20that%2031%25%20of%207-%20to%209-year-olds%20use%20X%20for%20an%20average%20of%209%20minutes%20a%20day.%20Really%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22knotopoulos%40businessinsider.com%20(Katie%20Notopoulos)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsecond-graders-using-x-parental-controls-2024-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bikaji%20Foods%20International%20acquires%20majority%20stake%20of%2055%25%20in%20Ariba%20Foods%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724414400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-05%2F08%2Fthumb%2Ffeaturecrop%2F400X400%2F1715141532-6314.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fbikaji-foods-international-acquires-majority-stake-of-55-in-ariba-foods-124082300707_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWith%20our%20advanced%20production%20facilities%20and%20export%20expertise%2C%20we%20are%20well-positioned%20to%20meet%20Bikaji's%20production%20needs