ollywood-releases-in-india%2Farticleshow%2F112729151.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tale%20of%20two%20hugs%3A%20PM%20Modi's%20'Bharat%20first'%20policy%20on%20display%20in%20Ukraine%20visit%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724412168000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-112739573%2Cimgsize-1015249.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Ftale-of-two-hugs-and-pm-modis-bharat-first-policy-amid-russia-ukraine-war%2Farticleshow%2F112739503.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Night%20Before%20Kolkata%20Doctor%20Was%20Raped%20And%20Murdered.%20What%20CBI%20Found%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFour%20colleagues%20of%20the%2031-year-old%20doctor%2C%20who%20was%20raped%20and%20murdered%20in%20Kolkata's%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%2C%20will%20be%20put%20through%20the%20lie-detector%20test%20because%20their%20statements%20are%20contradicting%20each%20other%2C%20sources%20from%20CBI%20have%20said.%20These%20include%20two%20first-year%20postgraduate%20trainees%2C%20a%20house%20surgeon%20and%20an%20intern.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20in%20the%20central%20agency%20have%20said%20that%20it%20doesn't%20appear%20that%20the%20four%20doctors%20were%20involved%20in%20crime%2C%20but%20it%20wants%20to%20check%20if%20they%20played%20a%20role%20in%20tampering%20with%20evidence%20or%20were%20part%20of%20a%20conspiracy.%20The%20investigators%20have%20also%20pieced%20together%20the%20sequence%20of%20events%20the%20night%20before%20the%20doctor%20was%20sexually%20assaulted%20and%20killed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Kolkata%20Police's%20timeline%20of%20events%2C%20one%20of%20these%20doctors%20saw%20the%20victim's%20body%20in%20the%20seminar%20hall%20around%209.30%20am%20the%20next%20day%20and%20alerted%20the%20authorities.%20All%20these%20four%20doctors%20had%20been%20questioned%20by%20the%20city%20police%20before%20CBI%20took%20over%20the%20probe%2C%20the%20timeline%20reveals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Has%20CBI%20Found%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20has%20found%20fingerprints%20of%20two%20of%20these%20four%20doctors%20in%20the%20third-floor%20seminar%20room%20where%20the%20body%20was%20found.%20A%20CCTV%20camera%20had%20captured%20the%20house%20surgeon%20going%20from%20first%20floor%20to%20the%20third%20floor%20that%20night.%20The%20house%20surgeon%20has%20said%20that%20he%20went%20to%20the%20third%20floor%20at%202.45%20am%20that%20night.%20The%20intern%20was%20on%20the%20third%20floor%20and%20had%20spoken%20to%20the%20victim%20that%20night%2C%20the%20CBI%20has%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Happened%20That%20Night%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20sources%2C%20the%20victim%20and%20two%20first-year%20postgraduate%20trainees%20had%20dinner%20around%20midnight.%20Then%20they%20went%20to%20the%20seminar%20room%20and%20watched%20Neeraj%20Chopra's%20javelin%20event%20at%20the%20Olympics.%20Around%202%20am%2C%20the%20two%20colleagues%20went%20to%20the%20sleep%20room%20where%20doctors%20on%20duty%20rested.%20The%20victim%20stayed%20back%20in%20the%20seminar%20room.%20The%20intern%20has%20said%20that%20he%20was%20in%20the%20interns'%20room.%20All%20these%20three%20rooms%20--%20the%20seminar%20hall%2C%20the%20sleep%20and%20the%20interns'%20room%20are%20located%20close%20to%20each%20other%20on%20the%20third%20floor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Morning%20After%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%209.30%20am%2C%20one%20of%20the%20postgraduate%20trainee%20doctors%2C%20with%20whom%20the%20victim%20had%20dinner%20the%20night%20before%2C%20went%20to%20look%20for%20her%20before%20the%20ward%20rounds%20began.%20He%20found%20%26quot%3Bher%20body%20in%20motionless%20state%20from%20a%20distance%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20Kolkata%20Police%20timeline%20says.%20He%20then%20informed%20his%20colleagues%20and%20senior%20doctors%20who%20alerted%20hospital%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Lie-Detector%20Test%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20has%20got%20permission%20for%20conducting%20the%20lie-detector%20test%20on%20the%20four%20doctors%20and%20Dr%20Sandip%20Ghosh%2C%20former%20principal%20of%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%2C%20who%20has%20drawn%20fire%20for%20his%20handling%20of%20the%20situation.%20A%20special%20court%20gave%20the%20go-ahead%20for%20this%20yesterday.%20Lie%20detector%20test%20can%20only%20be%20conducted%20after%20a%20permission%20from%20the%20court%20and%20the%20consent%20of%20the%20suspect.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724412000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fl35tt0so_doctor-protest_625x300_23_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkolkata-doctor-rape-murder-rg-kar-medical-college-why-cbi-wants-lie-detector-test-for-kolkata-rape-murder-victims-colleagues-6401012%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Four%20colleagues%20of%20the%2031-year-old%20doctor%2C%20who%20was%20raped%20and%20murdered%20in%20Kolkata's%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%2C%20will%20be%20put%20through%20the%20lie-detector%20test%20because%20their%20statements%20are%20contradicting%20each%20other%2C%20sources%20from%20CBI%20have%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkolkata-doctor-rape-murder-rg-kar-medical-college-why-cbi-wants-lie-detector-test-for-kolkata-rape-murder-victims-colleagues-6401012%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Video%3A%20Devotees%20From%20Pune%20Visit%20Tirumala%20Temple%20Wearing%2025%20Kg%20Gold%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDevotees%20from%20Pune%20vi