20in%20annualized%20net%20revenue%2C%20said%20Guo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPasses'%20product%20roadmap%20is%20large.%20Drawing%20on%20her%20AI%20expertise%2C%20Guo%20aims%20to%20launch%20features%20such%20as%20AI-driven%20pricing%20to%20gauge%20the%20value%20of%20content%20and%20how%20much%20fans%20are%20willing%20to%20pay.%20She%20also%20plans%20to%20introduce%20a%20donation%20feature%2C%20allowing%20creators%20to%20contribute%20a%20portion%20of%20their%20earnings%20from%20Passes%20to%20nonprofits.%20Her%20long-term%20vision%20is%20for%20Passes%20to%20support%20%26quot%3Bcreators%20to%20become%20entrepreneurs%20and%20start%20creating%20generational%20wealth.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20single%20one%20of%20my%20creator%20friends%20always%20asks%20me%2C%20how%20do%20I%20get%20into%20building%20my%20own%20brand%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20stranger%20to%20building%20a%20brand%20herself%2C%20Guo%20is%20ready%20to%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flucy-guo-left-scale-ai-itch-build-startup-passes-2024-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724407204000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c7e35843b5e59d16b488a3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flucy-guo-left-scale-ai-itch-build-startup-passes-2024-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Lucy%20Guo%20cofounded%20the%20data%20labeling%20startup%20Scale%20AI%2C%20and%20now%20leads%20Passes%2C%20a%20startup%20helping%20creators%20monetize%20their%20audiences.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22smuppidi%40insider.com%20(Sri%20Muppidi)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A41%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flucy-guo-left-scale-ai-itch-build-startup-passes-2024-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20Is%201992%20Ajmer%20Sex%20Scandal%2C%20In%20Which%206%20Got%20Life%20For%20Raping%20100%20Girls%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20POCSO%20court%20in%20Rajasthan%20on%20Tuesday%20sentenced%20six%20men%20to%20life%20imprisonment%20in%20the%20Ajmer%20sex%20scandal%20case.%20One%20of%20the%20most%20disturbing%20criminal%20cases%20from%20the%20early%201990s%2C%20it%20involved%20the%20sexual%20exploitation%20and%20blackmailing%20of%20as%20many%20as%20100%20young%20schoolgirls%20in%20Ajmer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20six%20accused%2C%20identified%20as%20Nafees%20Chishti%2C%20Naseem%20alias%20Tarzan%2C%20Salim%20Chishti%2C%20Iqbal%20Bhati%2C%20Sohail%20Ghani%20and%20Syed%20Zameer%20Hussain%2C%20were%20found%20guilty%20of%20the%20heinous%20crimes.%20The%20court%20also%20imposed%20a%20fine%20of%20Rs%205%20lakh%20on%20each%20accused.%20Previously%2C%20nine%20others%20were%20jailed%20for%20life%20in%20the%20same%20case%20and%20four%20were%20acquitted%20by%20the%20high%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Ajmer%20Rape%20Case%201992%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%201992%20Ajmer%20gangrape%20case%2C%20known%20as%20the%20%26quot%3BAjmer%20blackmail%20%3Cem%3Ekaand%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20involved%20the%20gangrape%20and%20blackmail%20of%20multiple%20young%20women%2C%20with%20video%20recordings%20and%20photos%20used%20to%20silence%20them.%20The%20case%20exposed%20a%20toxic%20mix%20of%20political%20patronage%2C%20religious%20influence%2C%20impunity%2C%20and%20small-town%20glamour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20was%20first%20exposed%20by%20journalist%20Santosh%20Gupta%20in%20a%20local%20newspaper%2C%20%3Cem%3EDainik%20Navjyoti%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20April%201992.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accused%2C%20including%20the%20influential%20Chishty%20duo%20of%20Farooq%20and%20Nafis%2C%20associated%20with%20the%20Ajmer%20Sharif%20Dargah%2C%20and%20their%20associates%2C%20exploited%20and%20gang%20raped%20scores%20of%20schoolgirls.%20A%20local%20photo%20lab%20printed%20and%20circulated%20nude%20pictures%20of%20the%20victims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20case%20came%20to%20light%2C%20religious%20tensions%20flared%20in%20Ajmer%2C%20leading%20to%20city-wide%20shutdowns.%20Despite%20the%20public%20outcry%2C%20the%20identities%20and%20whereabouts%20of%20the%20survivors%20remained%20unknown.%20Many%20victims%20came%20from%20modest%2C%20middle-class%20families%20of%20government%20employees%20but%20were%20misleadingly%20labelled%20as%20%3Cem%3E%26quot%3BIAS-IPS%20ki%20betiyan%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20(daughters%20of%20IAS%20and%20IPS%20officers)%2C%20by%20the%20media.%20Several%20families%20fled%20Ajmer%20in%20the%20aftermath%2C%20seeking%20refuge%20from%20the%20stigma%20and%20trauma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELawyers%20said%20that%20Section%20273%20of%20the%20Criminal%20Procedure%20Code%20required%20survivors%20to%20testify%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20the%20accused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20records%2C%20though%20incomplete%2C%20reveal%20the%20survivors'%20first%20names%20and%20outdated%20addresses%2C%20making%20it%20challenging%20to%20maintain%20contact.%20For%20over%2030%20years%2C%20the%20constant%20summons%20to%20court%2C%20often%20accompanied%20by%20policemen%20arriving%20at%20their%20doorstep%2C%20became%20a%20painful%20reminder%20of%20the%20ordeal%20for%20the%20victims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20now%20a%20grandmother%2C%20leave%20me%20alone.%20We%20have%20families.%20What%20do%20we%20tell%20them%3F%26quot%3B%20cried%20a%20gangrape%20survivor%20back%20in%202021%20after%20being%20summoned%20to%20court%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20the%20police%20were%20frustrated.%20In%202022%2C%20SHO%20Dalbeer%20Singh%2C%20tasked%20with%20delivering%20summons%20for%20about%20a%20year%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdefence.pk%2Fthreads%2Fgangraped-in-teens-visiting-courts-as-grandmothers-1992-ajmer-horror-is-an-open-wound.747556%2F%C2%A0%5C%22%3Eshared%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20emotional%20toll%20on%20the%20survivors%2C%20%26quot%3BHow%20many%20times%20will%20we%20drag%20them%20to%20court%3F%20On%20phone%20calls%2C%20they%20abuse%20us.%20Every%20time%20they%20see%20a%20policeman%20at%20their%20doors%2C%20they%20get%20terrified.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDescribing%20the%20experience%20as%20%26quot%3Bone%20hell%20of%20a%20task%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20revealed%20the%20heartbreaking%20consequences%20of%20repeatedly%20forcing%20survivors%20to%20relive%20their%20trauma.%20One%20family%20reported%20that%20their%20daughter%20had%20died%2C%20possibly%20due%20to%20the%20emotional%20toll%2C%20and%20another%20family%20sent%20a%20lawyer%20to%20intimidate%20him.%20At%20least%20three%20victims%20attempted%20suicide%20after%20recording%20their%20statements%20in%20court.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20sacked%20Rajasthan%20minister%20Rajinder%20Gudha%20alleged%20that%20Congress%20leaders%2C%20including%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Ashok%20Gehlot%2C%20were%20involved%20in%20the%20scandal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202023%20Hindi%20movie%2C%20%3Cem%3EAjmer%2092%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20is%20also%20based%20on%20the%20infamous%20Ajmer%20sex%20scandal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724407140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fln4k943c_ajmer-rape-accused_625x300_23_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-is-the-1992-ajmer-sex-scandal-in-which-6-got-life-term-for-raping-100-girls-6400467%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%201992%20Ajmer%20gangrape%20case%2C%20known%20as%20the%20%26quot%3BAjmer%20blackmail%20kaand%2C%26quot%3B%20involved%20the%20gangrape%20and%20blackmail%20of%20multiple%20young%20women%2C%20with%20video%20recordings%20and%20photos%20used%20to%20silence%20them.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-is-the-1992-ajmer-sex-scandal-in-which-6-got-life-term-for-raping-100-girls-6400467%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Karnataka%20Woman%20Wanted%20Rs%206.16%20Lakh%20In%20Alimony%20Per%20Month.%20Court%20Said...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20woman's%20demand%20for%20Rs%206.16%20lakh%20per%20month%20in%20alimony%20-%20including%20Rs%2060%2C000%20for%20monthly%20expenses%20(and%20a%20separate%20amount%20for%20dining%20expenses)%2C%20Rs%2050%2C000%20in%20legal%20fees%2C%20Rs%2015%2C000%20to%20buy%20clothes%20-%20was%20reportedly%20knocked%20back%20Wednesday%20by%20a%20single-judge%20bench%20of%20the%20Karnataka%20High%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20widely-shared%20video%20recording%20of%20court%20proceedings%20Justice%20Lalitha%20Kanneganti%20refused%20the%20request%2C%20and%20told%20the%20woman's%20counsel%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20she%20wants%20to%20spend%20(this%20much%20money)%2C%20let%20her%20earn.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Fhigh-court%2Fkarnataka-high-court%2Fkarnataka-high-court-questions-estranged-wife-expense-interim-maintenance-plea-hearing-267391%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBar%20and%20Bench%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20woman%20wanted%20more%20than%20the%20Rs%2050%2C000%20she%20is%20receiving%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReports%20said%20the%20woman%20claimed%20lakhs%20in%20alimony%20because%20her%20ex-husband%20wears%20expensive%20clothes%20and%20spends%20over%20Rs%2010%2C000%20per%20month%20on%20his%20wardrobe.%20The%20ex-wife%2C%20her%20lawyer%20argued%2C%20should%20therefore%20be%20given%20a%20similar%20budget%3B%20the%20woman%20declared%20her%20current%20wardrobe%20full%20of%20%26quot%3Bold%20clothes%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPart%20of%20the%20alimony%20demand%2C%20reports%20also%20said%2C%20included%20Rs%204-5%20lakh%20for%20medical%20bill%2C%20which%20includes%20treatment%20and%20physiotherapy%20for%20knee%20pain%20that%20was%20attributed%20to%20the%20ex-husband's%20%26quot%3Bnegligence%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%2C%20however%2C%20was%20unimpressed.%20According%20to%20legal%20news%20website%20Bar%20and%20Bench%2C%20Justice%20Kanneganti%20asked%2C%20%26quot%3BDoes%20anybody%20spend%20this%20much%3F%20A%20single%20lady%20(by)%20herself...%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20did%20not%2C%20though%2C%20dismiss%20the%20demand%20for%20alimony%2C%20and%20called%20on%20the%20woman%20to%20present%20a%20more%20reasonable%20account%20of%20expenses.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20want%20an%20order...%20I%20want%20actual%20figures%2C%20not%20this%20'lakhs%20of%20rupees'.%20Otherwise%20I%20will%20dismiss%20your%20application%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20was%20quoted%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Flet-her-earn-why-karnataka-hc-denied-rs-6-lakh%2Fmonth-alimony-to-woman%2Farticleshow%2F112715844.cms%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20was%20also%20warned%20against%20trying%20to%20%26quot%3Bexploit%20the%20process%20of%20the%20court%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20according%20to%20the%20above%20report%2C%20she%20was%20also%20ticked%20off%20for%20trying%20to%20bargain%20with%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYour%20client%20is%20not%20understanding...%20you%20(her%20lawyer)%20should%20understand%20and%20advise%20her.%20This%20is%20not%20a%20place%20for%20bargaining.%20You%20are%20supposed%20to%20tell%20the%20court%20her%20actual%20expenses.%20We%20will%20give%20you%20one%20last%20chance%20to%20be%20reasonable...%20else%20straightaway%20we%20will%20dismiss%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20declared.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%20is%20now%20available%20on%20WhatsApp%20channels.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatsapp.com%2Fchannel%2F0029Va4lixw7z4kcvZI9JM12%5C%22%3EClick%20on%20the%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20all%20the%20latest%20updates%20from%20NDTV%20on%20your%20chat.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724407020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2016-09%2Fjudge-court-generic-istock_650x400_81473483517.jpg%22%2C%22originI