%20out%20of%20bamboo%2C%20mud%2C%20wood%20and%20cow%20dung%20along%20with%20a%20small%20percent%20of%20concrete.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsk%20Deka%20what%20has%20been%20used%20to%20build%20the%20homes%2C%20and%20he%20responds%20%E2%80%9CEverything%20you%20can%20think%20of.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%20probing%20reveals%20bamboo%2C%20wood%2C%20straw%2C%20mud%2C%20cow%20dung%2C%20a%20small%20percentage%20of%20concrete%20bricks%2C%20cement%2C%20and%20corrugated%20sheets%20come%20under%20the%20umbrella%20of%20%E2%80%9Ceverything%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20basis%20of%20choosing%20these%20materials%20is%20dependent%20on%20their%20availability%20and%20also%20the%20practicality%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20while%20every%20person%20with%20a%20sustainable%20bend%20of%20mind%20starts%20out%20wanting%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F335976%2Fmumbai-sustainable-home-ecofriendly-mud-architecture-geeli-mitti-ngo-lakhichand-jain%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebuild%20a%20home%20using%20only%20mud%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20calculated%20decisions%20need%20to%20be%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20homestay%2C%20the%20furniture%20is%20handmade.%20The%20bamboo%20and%20cane%20pieces%20were%20made%20in%20Nagaland%20while%20the%20curtains%20were%20handwoven%20in%20the%20studio.%20The%20mirrors%20and%20shelves%20were%20made%20by%20local%20artisans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fkaziranga-homestay-12-1724336234.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20decor%20and%20furnishings%20at%20the%20Medini%20Homestay%20are%20an%20ode%20to%20the%20local%20artistry%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F