20then%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20looking%20back.%20She%20slowly%20gained%20her%20confidence%20back%20and%20started%20practice%20in%20earnest%20for%20the%20challenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20big%20challenge%20to%20tackle%20was%20the%20cold%20conditions%20of%20the%20English%20Channel.%20To%20get%20acclimatised%20to%20cold%20water%2C%20Tanvi%20first%20started%20taking%20only%20cold%20showers.%20She%20also%20started%20sitting%20in%20ice%20baths%20for%20half%20an%20hour%2C%20which%20later%20increased%20to%20one%20hour.%20%E2%80%9CI%20would%20sit%20in%20ice%20water%20from%202%20am%20to%203%20am%20to%20get%20used%20to%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Tanvi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-49-1723815126.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tanvi%20found%20happiness%20in%20swimming%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-49-1723815126.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-49-1723815126-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-49-1723815126-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-49-1723815126-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-49-1723815126-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-361699%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ETanvi%20found%20happiness%20in%20swimming.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20practised%20in%20Nainital%E2%80%99s%20Naini%20lake%20for%20a%20week%2C%20which%20has%20conditions%20simil